race.comment: Wide open. THE MARINER (6) gave a sight over the border last time when just nabbed late. Has the claim and inside gate and plenty of pressure coming out with scratchings. Going well and will take catching. SMART RETURN (12) has been ticking along okay and is a third-up winner. Back a notch and gets a chance to find form. WARMOSA (7) is another third-up and comes into this off a last start win. Among the main chances.  LONELY ONE(3) was outdated fresh then sat closer and was too good second-up. Has a winning record third-up and placed only try at the course and distance. Will be prominent and among the leading chances again.
